Charles Sutton is a data professional supporting analytics projects at Sharecare. He brings 10+ years of experience for companies such as Petco, Intuit, and Redbox. At Sharecare, he is evangelizing the power of analytics by working with business stakeholders to adopt and utilize analytical tools. Spending his career aligning analytics with business goals, his primary area of professional interest is creating clear and informative dashboard reports that support the sales, operations, and customer support functions.

Charles holds an MBA from Colorado State University, where he also received a certification in business intelligence. He is a proud husband and father that lives in the San Diego area with his wife, child, and dog Skipper. As an avid sports fan, he can always be found watching sports on the weekends.
